import React from 'react'
import {HeaderContainer, ImgContainer, HeaderButton} from './styled'
import pokemonLogo from '../../assets/images/pokemonLogo.png'
import pokeball from '../../assets/images/pokeball.svg'

const Header = () => {
    return(
        <HeaderContainer>
            
                < ImgContainer src={pokemonLogo}/>
                < ImgContainer src={pokeball}/>
            
            
            <HeaderButton>
                texto do button
            </HeaderButton>
            
        </HeaderContainer>
    )
}
export default Header
